{"tid":2287941,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[pxxfxxt hair/ 髮神(經)] 保證無效，你問我答","createTime":"2020-11-16T06:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T21:19:05.000Z","uid":351320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54ed5c2ad88ea53fd717189b626432a4b5e9dccf","tid":2287941,"uid":351320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"小弟疫情期間，比左差不多10萬去呢間嘢做。<br />\n被人狂sell就唔洗講，<br />\n無論對頭髮任何一方面，都完全無效。<br />\n<br />\n防脱髮？ 無<br />\n<br />\n生髮？ 無<br />\n<br />\n療程未做完就狂sell，唔肯繼續比錢就將依家啲療程hea做，<br />\n例如有個頭髮精華，平時大大pat塗得好足，有按摩，如果唔聽佢sell同唔再比錢就輕輕抹一抹就同我講bye bye。<br />\n<br />\n呢間嘢搵咁多明星去欺騙消費者，我唔似你哋咁無良心，我目的好簡單，<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔想再有受害者</span>。<br />\n<br />\n為免大家覺得我係惡意指控，如果有同路人想集體向消費者委員會投訴，歡迎一齊合作。<br />\n<br />\n我比你哋笑唔緊要，懇請大家傳開去。"},{"pid":"dc7ef6fc33a82902c5b96ff8b686253ebb6a5379","tid":2287941,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘<br />\n<br />\n10皮夠你植大部份位"},{"pid":"57f56d5424547e479ca6a716c7b09d487bbfcb1f","tid":2287941,"uid":351320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc7ef6fc33a82902c5b96ff8b686253ebb6a5379","tid":2287941,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘<br />\n<br />\n10皮夠你植大部份位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"總之